Canon Rebel T5 Sensor Cleaning /!/ Hey all,

I posted on this sub recently, and everyone was able to help me figure out that my sensor was dirty. I tried to clean my sensor, but with multiple attempts, no success. I recognize that the Canon Rebel T5 does not have an automatic sensor cleaning feature, so I was wondering what else I should be doing to clean my sensor. I've tried air blower and a sensorklear pen. Maybe I'm cleaning the wrong spot? Thanks in advance everyone.
